Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:20:03.46,CN_song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}人們為什麼要互相傷害 爭鬥不休呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.14,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:58.87,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 你超越了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:01.18,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是值得自豪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.54,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.19,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.38,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說 應該有能做的事才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:32.35,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.33,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 在那裡跟他聯手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:38.39,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,會變成什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.88,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:46.04,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是 一生才有一次的冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:51.18,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天開始 又回到了日常生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:57.40,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 還有一件事情 這個班將有一個新同學加入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:58.64,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:01.46,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.44,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.29,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這是楪祈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.17,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.02,CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:25.87,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,500)\an2}你不再愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:32.39,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}也不再需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:41.01,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}徒留我一人 孤零零在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:49.11,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}當初你說過什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:55.78,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}模糊的話語在空中消散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.09,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}我明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:02.48,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}今天卻還是許下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:09.00,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}無法實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.31,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}不要鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:19.13,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}緊緊地 交握雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:25.47,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}說會永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:35.47,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}緊握的手依然溫暖
